This task includes the routines of performing three major tasks  
1.If Bluetooth is available, connect to it and handle communication.
2.If only WiFi is available, connect to WiFi and turn off Bluetooth.
3.If both WiFi and Bluetooth are available, connect to WiFi and ensure Bluetooth is disconnected.
